description: {"blocks":[{"key":"4m7kc","text":"Immunofluorescence protocol on paraffin-embedded rat brain sections ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
materials_text: {"blocks":[{"key":"ecfd9","text":"Reagents :","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":10},{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":0,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2lcb9","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"87vva","text":"- TBS 10X : Tris base 121.1g + NaCl 90g in 1L H2O.pH 7.4.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"db5kk","text":"- TBS 1X-Triton 0,5%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"89tdt","text":"- Xilen","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"38i1e","text":"- Ethanol : 100%, 95%, 70%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9ena6","text":"- Unmasking buffer epitopes : Citrate solution 10mM pH6.0","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"372lp","text":"- Blocking Buffer : TBS 1X + 5% NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3eehl","text":"- 1st Ab : Diluted in1X PBS +2%NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c04","text":"- 2nd Ab : Diluted in1X PBS +2%NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"60aqi","text":"- Endogenous peroxidase blocking solution : TBS 1x + 3% H2O2(30%) + 10% methanol","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"bb3pp","text":"Put the slides 30 min in the incubator at 60ºC","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"d098t","text":"Wash 3x3 min in xylene","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"brklr","text":"Wash 1x10 min in ethanol 100%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"1rruq","text":"Wash 1x10 min in ethanol 95%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"adibg","text":"Wash 1x5 min in ethanol 70%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9tcfj","text":"Wash 2x5 min in PBS 1X","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"64sis","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"b1sin","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":0,"style":"bold"}],"key":"aurl7","text":"IMPORTANT: The buffer used for immunofluorescence is PBS,  not TBS as for immunohistochemistry and the endogenous peroxidase blocking step is not required.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"36api","text":"Add 200 mL/section of citrate buffer 10mM, pH 6","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"dq000","text":"Put sections in a boiling water bath for 20 min","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"8ljbc","text":"Let sections cool down for 20 min at room temperature (RT)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"8cnc3","text":"Wash 3x5 min in PBS 1X-Triton (0.5%)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"4ks4a","text":"Put wet paper in a black box for immunohistochemistry","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9f6gn","text":"Gently dry and circle sections with the hydrophobic pen ImmEdge Vector H 4000 without touching the tissue ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5p4j0","text":"Add 200 uL/section of blocking solution (5% NGS (in PBS 1X) (200uL/section) +  0.1% Triton (in PBS 1X)) 1h at RT","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"4popq","text":"Gently wipe off the water ofthe slides","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9fora","text":"Put 200ul/section of 1ary antibody in 2% NGS + 0.1% Triton overnight at 4ºC (cold room)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"em9t8","text":"Wash 3x5min in PBS 1X-Triton (0.5%)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"5o2qf","text":"Gently wipe off the water ofthe slides","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"f6lcm","text":"Put 200ul/section of 2ary antibody in 2% NGS + 0.1% Triton + DAPI for 1 h at RT","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7n8da","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"dqud7","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f1upj","text":"Alexa goat anti-mouse 488 (green color) 1:500 or 1: 1000, Alexa goat anti-rabbit 594 (red color) and 1:5000 DAPI (nuclei staining in blue color) ","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"16c14","text":"Wash 3x5min in PBS 1X ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ficnc","text":"Mount sections with fluorescent mounting medium. Put the coverslip (washed with ethanol previously) on the slide. Remove bubbles","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4rj22","text":"Let dry the slides on the tray in the hood for 5 minutes and store at 4ºC asap","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":74,"length":4}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
